        "description": "Applied loads, kinematics, and lubricant conditions in the FE model must correspond to ISO 14243-1 displacement-controlled knee simulator protocol within documented tolerances (±5% load, ±1 degree angle)."
      },
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions replicate ISO 14243-1 displacement-controlled protocol. Applied peak load 1000 N (±3%), flexion profile matches standard waveform within ±0.8 degrees. Bovine serum lubrication modelled via effective friction coefficient calibrated from simulator data. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
