        "description": "Validation experiments must use the same tibial insert geometry (within manufacturing tolerances), same UHMWPE material lot, and same ISO 14243-1 loading protocol as the intended COU."
      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on production-representative tibial inserts (same geometry file, same GUR 1050 material lot, gamma-irradiated and barrier-packaged per clinical specification) under ISO 14243-1 loading. No geometric or material surrogates used. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
