      "rationale": "Independent peer review conducted by a second FE analyst not involved in model construction. Review checklist covers boundary conditions, material assignments, contact pair definitions, and UMESHMOTION wear law parameters. Three minor discrepancies identified and corrected prior to final runs. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
