        "name": "Model inputs: material properties and wear coefficient sourced from traceable measurements",
        "description": "UHMWPE elastic modulus, Poisson ratio, and Archard wear coefficient must be sourced from traceable material characterisation tests (tensile testing per ASTM F648, pin-on-disk per ASTM G99) with documented uncertainty."
      },
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus 935 MPa (±42 MPa, n=10 tensile tests per ASTM F648), Poisson ratio 0.46 (literature consensus). Archard wear coefficient k=2.1×10⁻⁷ mm³/(N·mm) (±0.4×10⁻⁷, n=6 pin-on-disk tests per ASTM G99 on same material lot). All inputs traceable to test reports archived in the submission dossier. Achieved level 3 (traceable measurements with quantified uncertainty) exceeds required level 2."
