        "description": "Material properties, geometry, and loading parameters used in the FE model must be shown to be equivalent to those used in the validation simulator experiments within documented measurement uncertainty."
      },
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency table prepared mapping each FE input parameter to the corresponding simulator test measurement. Geometry equivalency confirmed by CMM measurement of test inserts vs. CAD nominal (max deviation 0.03 mm). Loading equivalency confirmed by load cell calibration records. Wear coefficient equivalency confirmed by pin-on-disk tests on same material lot. All equivalencies documented in the V&V plan. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
